channel.title: STAND WITH ME- V/M (collab?)
channel.description:
Hey everybody! My newest song, STAND WITH ME, is in the process of creating and I was wondering if anyone would like to collaborate on it with me. DM me if you are interested.
The demo is here: https://app.auxy.co/projects/plz98bghvng-Lx4B8M-QRw== The acoustic version is right here: https://app.auxy.co/projects/i9RCPDwXFVpmVyfiK0A2vg== I know what you’re thinking. This isn’t the best. But that’s why I need a collaborator on this.
